{"tid":2233494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地呢班人，疫情肆虐仲如期擺酒？","createTime":"2020-10-07T07:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T09:29:42.000Z","uid":36563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d91c49ec1a96a81cfcf64a614382edd060128a0","tid":2233494,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"[代cd-rom Fd Post]<br />\n<br />\n話說有個fd嚟緊結婚，上年已經搵咗間deco叫<strong>L_ve Opti_n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個Fd因為疫情 所以擺酒改期啦<br />\n點知比間deco公司話要收1000改期費<br />\n新期係旺季仲要再收1000<br />\n但佢話佢個plan都係一萬有找<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢另外啲攝影化妝花車公司，甚至再問出面其他deco，都一間要收呢啲疫情改期費用<br />\n<br />\n後尾佢仲上網見到原來都有唔少人中咗伏，寧願撻訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢見嚟緊又有婚展，想叫我幫佢開post提吓大家唔好中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外以下係佢係網上見到有人開既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>疫情下沒人情味的 大會指定佈置公司</strong><br />\n<br />\n2019婚展時俾左decoration deposit <br />\n<br />\n點知依家疫情咁嚴重，問有冇得extend，佈置公司話只可以半年內用，仲要比行政費用等雜費。 <br />\n但其實全世界都知疫情冇可能咁快停。 <br />\n<br />\n唉！信錯咗佢，講到話係連續幾次結婚展大會指定婚禮佈置公司，一啲人情味都冇，擺明R哂d錢。<br />\n<br />\n1) 如果客人取消婚禮或未能確定新日子，客人可以選擇取消訂單，會視為撻訂，所有已付款項一概不會退款。到客人有確定日子，客人可以以9折優惠價重新參加佈置套餐。<br />\n<br />\n2) 公司只接受*一次性*改期，改期時間為期big day半年之內，需要收返$1000行政費。如果新改期日子為九月至三月，要另付旺季特別附加費$1000。如果客人改期通知，最遲要兩個星期之前通知，少於兩星期通知，需$1000附加費。如果日子超過半年，公司有權收取另外附加費。建議客人提早通知我們，及按自己需要選擇日子。<br />\n如到big day 前2星期最後也夾不了日子，就會視為取消訂單，都不設退款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://wow.esdlife.com/space.php?uid=168615&amp;do=blog&amp;id=436990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwow.esdlife.com%2Fspace.php%3Fuid%3D168615%26do%3Dblog%26id%3D436990&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=3f6d7133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wow.esdlife.com/space.php?uid=168615&amp;do=blog&amp;id=436990</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps 個fd係cd rom，得個netvigator email冇得開ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d421f34f8df75bb7f7fcdcad78bb25e788ab5824","tid":2233494,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef65ab63fc3e706577b9b76985921001276146d4","tid":2233494,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e5f7684b47c68fefd0048d0f4e8ee11f7a6c0a","tid":2233494,"uid":6986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"呢行真係屈機 收到訂點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4a978c6679ac8b9654a8eac2c8dda4dc9ebc02","tid":2233494,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2e5f7684b47c68fefd0048d0f4e8ee11f7a6c0a","tid":2233494,"uid":6986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"呢行真係屈機 收到訂點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"係，個fd話比咗半訂，但都諗住撻<br />\n驚間嘢到時改期又再收幾千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169d1b1fa8f65a0e2708eddead0ca1c54c3aabcd","tid":2233494,"uid":300782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:32:17.000Z","msg":"香港人講法治都係得啖笑"},{"pid":"00ef3df16aae74e38c1f118db55bf5f8fccecbbb","tid":2233494,"uid":44783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af4a978c6679ac8b9654a8eac2c8dda4dc9ebc02","tid":2233494,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2e5f7684b47c68fefd0048d0f4e8ee11f7a6c0a","tid":2233494,"uid":6986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"呢行真係屈機 收到訂點都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"